 Love your neighbors folks.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fWCtiRe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rCbA3Wv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>(Swoons)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0bzJLCf.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UwJurld.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4YjfrIQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Love and miss you Space Mom.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1gVoIfK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vzicNho.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Louder for the people in the back.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tMphV8N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The old world is dying, the new one struggles to be born. Now is the time of monsters.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6aPG3jH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PvHNaqR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Always remember that the urge to sing “the lion sleeps tonight“ is only just a whim away, a whim away, a whim away…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/72AZRSm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>…realizing I’m an NPC because I repeat the same few phrases, have repetitive tasks, and frequently bump into walls/doors.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oBM5tIZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eqPVWhK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iHrifZJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Makes me think of Joker’s song from The Laughing Joke.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BIxRo24.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The struggle is real.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OJSn4xp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b2oYWB0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1yKK4iV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What do you say when someone approaches you…? The audacity.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6FE7cO6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If the pizza man truly loves this babysitter why does he keep slapping her rear?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b0aJxn9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Soul worth about $3.50</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QgVF4gc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Now I can only hear it in Simlish.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sticSRu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Being kind to one another is punk as fuck.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hCKKBxA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Seriously, all these billionaires and no superheroes… Just Wish Lex Luther</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O4EOm8y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Lower Decks. Out of all the sci-fi I love Star Trek the most because it has hope.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KtQGSWc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sign me up tin man!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KcHoYuA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/apAqKXL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Doors are the real BBEG.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JFil3PM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Joker didn’t realize that Red Skull is an actual Nazi and it’s not some shtick so he stops what he’s doing and fights him. Be like Joker.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/B7oYcZ5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2dJuLzC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fun fact: The line from Midnight Cowboy was improvised when a real New York City cab driver drove through the shot while Hoffman and his co-star were crossing the street.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KgD10M4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Jm9IT1m.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You merely adopted neurospiciness. I was born into it, molded by it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/G5f6T62.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They make the rockin’ world go ‘round.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EznRDpw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ren & Stimpy for me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KSdLGb6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fun fact #2: his tongue sucking gesture was also improvised.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4OdEtAk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But the ocean has meat and veggies and is cold…the ocean is gazpacho, change my mind.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/au1N1yT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fuck yeah they do!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5vKC6nd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Thanks for your time. Hope your day is effulgent.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5PF64Lm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DaymanAhAAAAah]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Look at her watch.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ywR2Caj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xukowSQ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ywR2Caj</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WeirdAlisMySpiritUserName]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>5 Stahs.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Dp00oyW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/opURgL3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Dp00oyW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>100 year old record played on a 102 year old gramophone</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CLWX7LK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PnXj2yU.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CLWX7LK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DALLASLAVOWNER]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Working on getting stronger.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/3Pdnqvq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/47nAYP2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It wasn't perfect to but by the end it was much better.  I hope everyone is having a great day and has a wonderful weekend.  Thank you I really appreciate the encouragement and support.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/3Pdnqvq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kaosnole95]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A gangster’s fruit cutting skills</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0meb6Io</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4a3Q4M9.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0meb6Io</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mysticciphers]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Electricity</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uM1Glv5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HPIP4sm.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That's not me, it's Carolyn Rupp. She IS the groove.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uM1Glv5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheOneWhoWasLeft]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It will get worse before it gets better</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4t8xGgm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dl94PkJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MQ9kQRj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qfYGEZt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pDTEinC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GTV6Mf7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/akuSpoB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>When I was little, I didn't know I wasn't supposed to be here. My favorite hero was Captain Marvel because Superman was a ham handed overly preachy comic to me. But he was my brothers favorite hero, and as an adult, I know why. He made him feel a lot better and maybe these will make someone else feel better too.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4t8xGgm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[scamlikley]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>